  "text": "China, but also in the US. Each exposure metric is then related to RY using empirical relationships as listed in Table 1 . In these relationships, RY is the crop yield under conditions with ozone compared to conditions without ozone Following Van Dingenen et al. (2009) and [CITATION_1] , we use the mean of these metrics for each species to calculate the total production change due to ozone.",
